{"tid":638374,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如何有效地拒絕電話調査","createTime":"2018-04-22T15:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T10:07:44.000Z","uid":46000,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a24ed11498d0363c6d6ac94c2f25e5936b328628","tid":638374,"uid":46000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>一，取消固網電話</strong><br />\n好大部份嘅電話調査系統嘅抽樣都只係gen固網電話，唔想比人煩最徹底就係唔好再裝固網<br />\n<strong>二，唔好講「我唔得閒」</strong><br />\n除非你係真心想之後佢打嚟再做，如果唔係都唔好講自己係唔得閒而拒絕訪問。如果唔係，訪問員係會set你嘅number去callback，之後再打翻比你<br />\n以下係你可以講嘅嘢：<br />\n「我地唔接受訪問」<br />\n「唔好再打嚟」<br />\n「我地無興趣」<br />\n又或者tricky啲：<br />\n「依到公司電話嚟」<br />\n（講其他語言）<br />\n<strong>三，「喂」</strong><br />\n發覺有好多人聽電話唔會出聲喂先，聽唔到聲就收線。但其實咁樣訪問員有機會唔知接通咗，而較你嘅number去callback，打多次比你<br />\n<strong>四，明確拒絕</strong><br />\n點都講句唔洗啦唔該，無啦啦cut線訪問員可能會打多次比你<br />\n<br />\n而另外，你係有權：<br />\n<strong>要求提供資料核實訪問員身份</strong><br />\n佢通常可以提供電話比你問負責人，若打唔通該電話亦可要求與當晚主管對話<br />\n<strong>問下大概要幾耐</strong><br />\n如果你想幫手但又趕時間最好就問下，如果唔係做做下先cut線反而嘥咗你自己時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong>拒絕提供個人資料</strong><br />\n但其實大學嘅調査機構嚟講，電話係隨機抽樣再做一啲加減程序，唔會知打咗去邊，連個到係公司定住宅都唔知，都無必要咁擔心<br />\n<strong>問清楚委託機構</strong><br />\n通常係intro就講咗，但係聽唔清楚就問多次穩陣"},{"pid":"e10d8be4336b4f9543de70b96133c262e3ed8687","tid":638374,"uid":105063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"cut 線"},{"pid":"30f2f1fce6eb9f17e60b8fdc2f3acd56a5249d4f","tid":638374,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e10d8be4336b4f9543de70b96133c262e3ed8687","tid":638374,"uid":105063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"cut 線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"你咁樣好咩？樓主打篇打左咁耐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a0a242eed5ce2ffff8f897b108365ed6ac327f","tid":638374,"uid":149041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"上次有間問香港公共事業 話五分鐘好快搞掂 點知做咗我三個字有多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n明明講話用中電佢都問我港炊啲嘢 點答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4959066a54afffdc02fc2e941875621ee5c788b","tid":638374,"uid":149041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次有間問香港公共事業 話五分鐘好快搞掂 點知做咗我三個字有多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n明明講話用中電佢都問我<span style=\"color: red;\">港燈</span>啲嘢 點答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f8586752bda7dc2f96a215405f83b513f542f703","tid":638374,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}